extendedInfo.description: Goldfish Wallpapers has 25 handpicked photos of goldfish! A goldfish is small member of the carp family that was domesticated in China over a thousand years ago. Share these images with your friends via Facebook, Twitter, email and text messaging. This small sized application was made especially for Android devices by Dreamtree Mobile. Please visit us at www.dreamtreemobile.com for more examples of wallpapers for Android devices. Rate us and comment! We love to hear about what you care about most!Thanks to:   Benson Kua, KenishiNobusue,  The Gian Vermin, OpenCage, Crezalyn Nerona Urutsuji, hapal for permission (cc) to use. All images are property of respective owners.Legal notice: We believe our images fall under the fair use doctrine as they are reduced size and excerpted for informational purposes.
